eight\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While India'smale hockey players dominated for decades, it took until 2008 for an individual Olympic champion to be unearthed, and Abhinav Bindra has been joined by only a single successor on the top step of the podium since.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1188, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Abhinav Bindra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abhinav_Bindra\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"India'smale hockey players\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual Olympic champion\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"only a single successor\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"the top step\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that man could be about to charm a nation as he defends his title atParis 2024.Neeraj Choprawas one of the breakthrough stars of Tokyo 2020, hurlinghimself into history with javelin gold.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1417, \"end\": 1422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9996413245548349, \"rank\": 0.00035879939466876076, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that man\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1296}, {\"ngram\": \"a nation\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"his title\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"Choprawas\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"the breakthrough stars\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"hurlinghimself\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1456}, {\"ngram\": \"javelin gold\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was an Olympic title that came not as a total surprise but nonetheless unexpectedly.\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic title\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"a total surprise\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1534}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chopra had emerged several years before Tokyo as a bright young star of field athletics, winning Commonwealth Games gold in 2018 before smashing the national record at the Asian Games.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9996413245548349, \"rank\": 0.00035879939466876076, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1662, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999430336316594, \"rank\": 4.719361296340452e-05, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chopra\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"a bright young star\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1633}, {\"ngram\": \"field athletics\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"the national record\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"the Asian Games\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there would soon be a setback.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a setback\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bone spurs in Chopra's throwing right elbow forced him to miss the 2019 World Championships, with the nature of the injury requiring surgery and a stylistic re-think.\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bone\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"Chopra's throwing right elbow\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2019 World Championships\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1877}, {\"ngram\": \"the nature\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"the injury\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"surgery\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"a stylistic re\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Joining forces with Klaus Bartoneitz, a German biomechanics expert, Chopra returned to international competition after 16 months out and set his sights on Olympic success.\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1993, \"end\": 1999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.7513741678987991, \"rank\": 0.3267610471666442, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"forces\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"Klaus Bartoneitz\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"Chopra\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"international competition\", \"from\": 2040, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"16 months\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"his sights\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic success\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On August 7, 2021, it was achieved.\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2161, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having laid down a marker by progressing through qualifying needing only a single throw, Chopra's first two throws of the final proved unsurpassable.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a marker\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifying\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"only a single throw\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My goal was always the Tokyo Olympics,\\\" Chopra said at the time.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My goal\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2321}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2351}, {\"ngram\": \"Chopra\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I put in the hard work and trusted the process since every single effort counts when it comes to success at the highest level.\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hard work\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2402}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"every single effort counts\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest level\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They say a lion always takes a step back before attacking.\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lion\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2524}, {\"ngram\": \"a step\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think of a setback in an athlete's life like that, so I ensured that I gave my 100 per cent during the rehab phase so that I could be at my best possible shape on return.\\\"\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a setback\", \"from\": 2579, \"to\": 2588}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete's life\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2609}, {\"ngram\": \"my 100 per cent\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2661}, {\"ngra